Based on our understanding of the term "sell" under the CCPA, we do not sell your personal information. You may directly revise, correct, or delete the personal information you provide via your Product Science user account. Alternatively, California residents may make a request at
support@productscience.ai
to exercise their rights, request copies of the data collected about them in the past 12 months, request that their personal information collected by Product Science be deleted, or to exercise their right to opt out.  Such request must include sufficient information to allow us to verify that you are the person (or such person’s agent) about whom we have collected personal information and describe your request in sufficient detail to allow us to understand, evaluate, and respond to it. Opt-out requests may be canceled by making an opt-in request via your user account or by contacting us at
support@productscience.ai
.  We will work to respond to your valid request within 45 days of receipt. We will not charge you a fee for making a valid request unless your valid request(s) is excessive, repetitive, or manifestly unfounded. If we determine that your valid request warrants a fee, we will notify you of the fee and explain that decision before completing your request.
